('minsan', 'Minsan', '/images/minsan.webp', '/images/minsan-banner.webp', '“Minsan” is a heartfelt reflection on friendship, nostalgia, and the bittersweet passage of time. It tells the story of people who once shared deep connections and carefree moments, only to drift apart as life moves forward.', '9.5', '2026', '5m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/minsan-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/minsan.webp', NULL, '/images/minsan-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, '/images/minsan-mobile-carousel.webp', NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/MINSAN_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/TRAILER.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/Minsan.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811369/Minsan-tall_etknbw.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('tindahan-ni-aling-nena', 'Tindahan ni Aling Nena', '/images/tindahan.webp', '/images/tindahan-detail.webp', 'A lively and colorful performance of “Tindahan ni Aling Nena” from Ang Huling El Bimbo, this scene brings energy and humor while subtly reflecting the group’s youthful bond and everyday life.', '9.7', '2026', '5m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/tindahan-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/tindahan.webp', NULL, '/images/tindahan-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/Tindahan/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, '/images/Tindahan-mobile-banner.webp', NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Tindahan_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Tindahan_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/Tindahan.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811310/Tindahan-tall_jxtnzf.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('alapaap-overdrive', 'Alapaap/Overdrive', '/images/alapaap.webp', '/images/alapaap-detail.webp', 'This high-octane performance of “Alapaap / Overdrive” captures the raw rebellion and fleeting freedom of youth. It’s an emotional escape fueled by the reckless energy that ultimately shapes the characters'' journey.', '9.8', '2026', '6m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/alapaap-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/alapaap.webp', NULL, '/images/alapaap-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/Alapaap/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Alapaap_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Alapaap_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/Alapaap.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811438/Alapaap-tall_nuyyqm.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('spoliarium-graduation', 'Spoliarium/Graduation', '/images/spoliarium.webp', '/images/spoliarium-detail.webp', 'The “Spoliarium/Graduation” sequence moves from the visceral trauma of Joy’s stolen innocence to the bitter irony of celebration. Marko’s ill-timed confession of love serves as a heartbreaking reminder of a future already shattered by the darkness preceding it.', '9.9', '2026', '5m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/spoliarium-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/spoliarium.webp', NULL, '/images/spoliarium-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/Spoliarium/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Spoliarium_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/Spoliarium_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/Spoliairum.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811337/Spoliarium-tall_huygnl.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('pare-ko', 'Pare Ko', '/images/pare-ko.webp', '/images/pare-ko-detail.webp', 'This high-energy ROTC sequence transforms military drills into a vibrant spectacle of brotherhood. Set to the iconic **“Pare Ko,”** it balances sharp choreography with the raw “friendzone” angst that defines the bond between the three leads.', '9.6', '2026', '6m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/pare-ko-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/pare-ko.webp', NULL, '/images/pare-ko-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/PareKo/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/PareKo_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/PareKo_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/PareKo.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811352/PareKo-tall_xrdjxa.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('tama-ka-ligaya', 'Tama Ka/Ligaya', '/images/tama-ka.webp', '/images/tama-ka-detail.webp', 'The “Tama Ka / Ligaya” mashup contrasts the finality of a breakup with the warmth of nostalgia. It masterfully captures the bittersweet irony of moving on while still clinging to a lost happiness.', '9.8', '2026', '4m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, '/images/tama-ka-mobile.webp', '/images/tama-ka-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/tama-ka.webp', '/images/tama-ka-mobile.webp', '/images/tama-ka-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/TamaKa/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/TamaKa_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/TamaKa_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/TamaKa.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811324/TamaKa-tall_uficjc.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
('ang-huling-el-bimbo', 'Ang Huling El Bimbo', '/images/huling-el-bimbo.webp', '/images/huling-el-bimbo-detail.webp', 'The heart-wrenching “Ang Huling El Bimbo” finale mirrors a graceful past against a tragic present. As a tribute to Joy, it captures the regret of a friendship ended too soon, closing the story with the haunting beauty of a dream that can never be reclaimed.', '9.9', '2026', '11m', ARRAY['Musical','Drama','Nostalgia','Ang Huling El Bimbo']::text[], 'PG-13', NULL, false, false, NULL, NULL, '/images/huling-el-bimbo-mobile.webp', '/images/huling-el-bimbo-detail-mobile.webp', '/images/huling-el-bimbo.webp', '/images/huling-el-bimbo-mobile.webp', '/images/huling-el-bimbo-logo.webp', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-3/ElBimbo/index.m3u8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/ElBimbo_TRAILER_MOBILE.mp4', 'https://boycanad.github.io/stream-storage-2/ElBimbo_TRAILER_MOBILE.vtt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '/images/clips/square/AngHulingElBimbo.webp', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dtzphltjc/video/upload/f_mp4,vc_h264,ac_aac/v1776811427/ElBimbo-tall_aixrsg.mp4', 'movie', NULL),
